data.description: Your perfect home awaits! This Nicholas Glen subdivision home is surrounded by nature & features hardwood floors, new carpets in bedrooms & living room (in August '23), new interior paint throughout, a cozy fireplace, & a kitchen w/stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, enjoy a versatile bonus room, a vaulted primary bedroom w/en-suite, plus 3 more bedrooms. Outside, relax on the expansive deck or the upstairs balcony, overlooking a lush backyard. Plus a workshop & extra-deep garage bay. New roof in 2022. RARE OPPORTUNITY! **HOME HAS AN ASSUMABLE 5.75% LOAN**Your perfect home awaits! This 2-story home in the Nicholas Glen subdivision, is surrounded by mature trees and offers a blend of traditional charm and modern comfort. The main floor features beautiful hardwood floors, leading to a living room featuring a gas fireplace with a custom-built mantel and new carpet, perfect for cozy evenings. The dining room, with its sliding glass doors, invites natural light and scenic views, extending to a well-equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances.A separate laundry room and a powder room are conveniently located downstairs. Upstairs, the home unfolds into a versatile bonus room, ideal for a home office or media room, enhanced by custom-built cabinets for optimal storage. The primary bedroom, with its vaulted ceiling and private bathroom, offers a peaceful retreat. Three additional bedrooms and a main bathroom are featured upstairs with new carpet throughout all bedrooms.The backyard is a private oasis, featuring an expansive deck overlooking the natural surroundings, ideal for relaxation or entertaining. An upstairs balcony adds an extra touch of outdoor enjoyment. The property also includes a 10 X 13 workshop with electricity, perfect for hobbies or storage, and a garage with an extra deep bay. All new carpeting was installed in August 2023 as well as new interior paint, and a new roof, installed in 2022 making this home truly turn-key!
